sun.misc

Class Hashing

  • java.lang.Object
    • sun.misc.Hashing

  • public class Hashing
extends Object
    this is a model class for sun.misc.Hashing, which is a Java 7 class we model to make JPF compile under Java 6. We provide a peer for this class since its highly repetitive bytecode will otherwise cause arithmetic overflow, which is a condition we might check for. The code would otherwise also lengthen traces, esp. during system initialization
